description: Sativa Rose visits our jail cell, where she experiences a bewildering variety of Mechanical Oddities. She starts out with the Priceless and the Rocker, then moves on to the heavy equipment: The Trespasser, the MiniMite, and finally the Predator in both doggy-style and missionary. It looks like she'll be back, judging from the look on her face...
title: Sativa Rose
